text: Papenkov () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Beloselskoye Rural Settlement of Koshekhablsky District, Adygea, Russia. The population was 26 as of 2018. There are 2 streets. == Geography == The khutor is 5 km south-east from Krasnogvardeyskoye and 3 km south-west from Preobrazhenskoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Koshekhablsky District
title: Papenkov
